mkdotenv (0.4.0-0debian1~unstable1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix alpine build.
  * Use variable-value parameter for setting the value as variable
    value.
  * Use variable-name parameter for setting the value as variable value.
  * [NEW FEATURE] Flag to remove multiple occurences of the variable.
  * [NEW FEATURE] Use - value upon in order to output modified .env
    contents upon stdout. Default behaviour is outputing upon .env

